locality: Ca. 2.0 km SW from the junction with the Sumbawanga-Mbala (Zambia) Road, on the road to Safu. In open grasslands and rocky miombo woodland slopes (granite). Collected with R.E. Gereau, B. Mhoro, M.J. Kayombo & M.A. Mwangoka.
Kanona District; Kundalila Falls Picnic Area ca. 13 km S of Serenje-Mpika Hwy. at Kanona. Collections in grasslands along stream. Rocky soils, quartz sand and basalt outcrops.
Eastern Province, Luangwa valley, Mwali Camp
Near Clouds Pool area, Gorongosa National Park, Muanza
